rows.label: qev087005_MSG0001
rows.name:
Is that the Ganglion data drive?
Excellent work. You have my thanks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087005_MSG0002
rows.name: Tatsu happy to get thanks, but MORE happy to get reward.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087005_MSG0003
rows.name:
Of course. I'll reward you for your efforts
with as large a sum as I'm able.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087005_MSG0004
rows.name: Next comes the task of decrypting and analyzing this data.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087005_MSG0006
rows.name:
I'm afraid not.
However, I might suggest letting a Ma-non take a look.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087005_MSG0007
rows.name: If you'd like, we can bring it to someone we know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087005_MSG0008
rows.name: I see. I leave it to you, then.[ST:wait ]
